<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.246341>
    dc:description "FIGURE 10. Final instar caterpillars of Pelopidas mathias mathias, dorsolateral view. 1, collected as penultimate instar caterpillar on Megathyrsus maximus, Mazoe Dam, near Harare, Zimbabwe, 25. iii. 1988; moulted to final instar 28. iii; photographed 13. iv.; pupated 22. iv.; ref. 99 / 26; 2, collected on maize, Kakamega, photographed 22. iv. 1988 (H. van den Berg)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/246341/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.246343>
    dc:description "FIGURE 12. Sixth instar caterpillars and pupa of Pelopidas thrax, collected on Saccharum sp. in Hajar Mountains, Oman, 17 Apr 1994 (after Cock 2010 a). 1, dorsal view of caterpillar, 35 mm; 2, detail of caterpillar head, anterolateral view; 3, detail of caterpillar head, anterior view (different individual); 4, pupa, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/246343/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.246342>
    dc:description "FIGURE 11. Pupa of Pelopidas mathias mathias, dorsal view; collected as penultimate instar caterpillar on Megathyrsus maximus, Mazoe Dam, near Harare, Zimbabwe, 25. iii. 1988; pupated 22. iv.; photographed 22. iv., 25 mm; adult 4. v.; ref. 99 / 26." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/246342/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

